frame_eqs_eel:
wave_r = wave_r + .14*(.26*sin(time*.555) + (sin(time*.222)));
wave_b = wave_b + .13*(.97*sin(time*.444) + (sin(time*.111)));
wave_g = wave_g + .15*(.51*sin(time*.666) + (sin(time*.333)));
